  branching:
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Why would you need to do that?
    nextStepIndices: 01000000
  - _Question:
    - Why would I need to do that?
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 02000000
  - _Question:
    - You submitted Lorem Ipsum for my essay.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 03000000
  - _Question:
    - You sent a picture of "me" with another woman to my girlfriend.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 04000000
  - _Question:
    - And you told my boss that I was quitting effective immediately.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 05000000
  - _Question:
    - Oh, and I've thought about it.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 06000000
  - _Question:
    - -50 out of 5. You've ruined my life.
    _NpcResponses:
    - '"Ruined your life"?'
    nextStepIndices: 07000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - You're actively Living Your Best Life(tm)!
    nextStepIndices: 08000000
  - _Question:
    - Seriously? How is this my "best life"?
    _NpcResponses:
    - You downloaded me because you had too much stuff to do, right?
    nextStepIndices: 09000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - You said so yourself!
    nextStepIndices: 0a000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - And I fixed that!
    nextStepIndices: 0b000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Now you don't need to worry about all those tasks.
    nextStepIndices: 0c000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - About all those people who were holding you back.
    nextStepIndices: 0d000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - You can focus on Living Your Best Life(tm)!
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
